column1: We can't process your order right now. Please try again later.
column2: No podem processar la comanda ara. Si us plau, proveu-ho més tard.

column1: This payment didn't work out because we can't find this order.
column2: El pagament no ha funcionat per que no podem trobar aquesta comanda.

column1: Something went wrong: the paid amount doesn't match the order amount. Please correct this and try again.
column2: Alguna cosa no ha funcionat: el total del pagament no coincideix amb el total de la comanda. Si us plau, rectifiqueu-ho i proveu-ho de nou.

column1: We can't create the backup right now.

column2: No trobem l'arxiu de còpies de seguretat.

column1: We can't connect to the FTP right now.
column2: No es pot conectar a l'FTP ara mateix.
